absence_type: Absence without reason or Official leave

title: Paula Oluwaseyi leave request
content:
Dear Sir,
This is to seek your kind permission to avail of a two-day casual leave from the office effective 8th of June 2020 until 9th June 2020. I need to make arrangements for our house transfer from Jabi to Lugbe on the above dates. I would resume work on the 10th of June. 
Thanking you in anticipation,
Yours Sincerely,
Oluwaseyi A Paula
